Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.52,0:00:06.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,离开这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:10.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,村里的人还在怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:12.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐是不是还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:14.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,苍乃还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:22.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我是作为祭品才来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:24.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为了平息夜祸作乱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:29.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 现在我和姐姐都不会相信那种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:30.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:32.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:36.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我一直都一个人 所以没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:38.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就算依人和苍乃不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:48.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,谁说我们不在了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.21,0:00:52.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,三个人一起离开这里吧 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:55.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,三个人 一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:56.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:58.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天和姐姐谈过了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:02.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,即使离开这里 也要和茉莉一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:05.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不要再说那样的话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.41,0:01:08.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:17.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:22.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,让一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:30.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一…二～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:18.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:20.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉突然来访
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:24.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想再一次好好和你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:30.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,选择离开这里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:35.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人选择了我 说要和我一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:39.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,听依人说了 他要让你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:41.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:47.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错 果然依人最先考虑的还是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:52.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不想让你悲伤 不想让你痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:54.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直都只考虑这些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:57.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我已经忍受不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜欢依人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:05.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,与依人邂逅 一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这样之后 果然不想分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得一个人很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:12.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,把依人给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:16.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你认真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:19.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我已经得到依人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人现在在我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:23.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们来决定谁能留在依人的身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我买了爆米花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:09.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你连这个都准备了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是真的要放什么电影咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,需要气氛 气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:21.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐 那个人会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,主人公最后一定会得到幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:31.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,脸被劈成两半了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是恐怖电影的设定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:36.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,果然约会看电影的话应该看恐怖的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:37.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不怎么喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:41.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:42.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:44.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:47.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啦 那下次试试看…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候去看一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:01.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:04.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想她应该会来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:06.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我说得有点过头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:07.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:11.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不 该抱歉的人应该是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我和苍乃之间的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,被卷进来的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个穿运动服的家伙有点可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看 行动起来很不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:24.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:28.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 那个脚上的污痕是刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:32.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是 那对情侣被袭击地方的泥土
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好像电影的类型变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛 原本是恐怖类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:39.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:45.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡是一种什么样的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:50.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢 虽然一直都活着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:53.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只有对这件事一无所知呢 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:06:58.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是空地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:07.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:30.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 你在吧 依人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这里附近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:36.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,即使我们战斗也毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:38.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,即使把我打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我失去了夜祸的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:43.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人就无法活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:45.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:46.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:51.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,把你打倒 然后让可怜的依人消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:57.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你认真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:20.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:24.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐没必要去死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:27.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那样做的话 大家会很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:28.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不能让你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:33.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我成为夜祸的祭品后 大家会幸福的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:51.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:57.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 太好了 你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:05.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 她是夜祸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:23.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的 是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:28.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为我是祭品 我却还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:31.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我没有死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:57.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,把依人还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:09:59.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:00.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的依人已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:04.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:07.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的依人在那个时候已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他不可以待在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:12.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我在那个时候也应该死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:14.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和依人一起消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:15.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:17.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,变成现在这样不是因为你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:22.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没有让你来帮我 你却 你却
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:26.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 所以我要把一切恢复到原样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:59.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 苍乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:08.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了不是一个人时是什么感受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:12.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,知道有人在身边时的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:15.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:28.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:40.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:47.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:49.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做到的只是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可以把死掉的人变成夜祸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:54.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:56.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我找过了 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:01.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么让我活过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:09.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想继续活在没有依人的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:30.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 不要走 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:33.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:38.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:12.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:42.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:48.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:50.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:55.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我不走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能跟姐姐一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:02.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉要让你消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:03.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:06.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是我拜托她的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:14.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我 我不是依人 什么都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我本是不该留在这里的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:21.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我要回到我原本的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和姐姐一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:25.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:26.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:27.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:29.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我消失了 依人消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:30.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就什么都不会留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里消失的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就会好像什么都没有发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:36.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那才是正确的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:39.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始我就不会做那样的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:42.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 有了夜祸的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:43.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想就可以做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:48.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想又可以和依人在一起生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:53.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说这是没有意义的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我悲伤痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:57.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,终于找到的你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说是没有意义的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:00.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:01.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:19.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我要快点去依人那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:36.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多已经开始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:38.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:42.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是你说想要喝果汁 我们才下来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:45.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,下一班车呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:47.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只有等头班车了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:49.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:51.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:53.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:01.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,担心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:02.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:05.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为茉莉已经下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:10.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是没有任何动摇和犹豫的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:12.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助也好 担心也好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:14.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,全都不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:19.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,她能做到 不管多么困难的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:20.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:28.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是那两个人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:43.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:45.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,结束后马上就放你下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:50.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果茉莉不在的话 我也不会跟姐姐走的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:53.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,强行也要把你带走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:55.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是姐姐的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:56.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:58.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是姐姐制造的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:00.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:05.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是真正的依人 我不会说这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:07.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的依人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:09.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,做了让姐姐感到不安的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也做过姐姐不希望他做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:16.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但那就是活着的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:19.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,有不如意的事 也有讨厌的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是阻止不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我的话可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:25.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦出事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:26.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以失去记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:28.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,当作什么都没有发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:29.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:30.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:32.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才觉得很空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:36.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:40.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是依人 我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:41.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:44.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:58.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:03.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们做个了结吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:08.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 正如我意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:20.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:35.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:39.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等着我 马上就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:54.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:20:00.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,让这一切都结束吧 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:01.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:13.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:15.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 放开我 依人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:44.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:46.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:47.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:05.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,往那把刀里倾注你的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:07.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,转移到夜祸人体内
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以变回人类
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:12.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,把苍乃变回人类
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.29,0:21:51.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以变回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:54.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:58.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:33.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,飞向天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:34.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,飞过天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:37.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,想证实自己并非一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:40.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,想知道漂浮的云朵的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:43.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,比任何人都虔诚地一直在祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:45.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空
